    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In Christi nomine. Breve memorie qualiter infra <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Churches">Lucense</placeName> civitate, prope <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/271" key="#Churches"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >ecclesiam</rs> Sancte Iulie</orgName>, in conspectu
                            <persName>Albertini Grechi</persName>, <persName>Schotti
                            Natalis</persName> quondam <persName key="#Judge">Fralmi <rs
                                key="#Judge">iudicis</rs></persName>,
                            <persName>Guiglielmus</persName> et <persName>Herighus</persName>
                        germani et filii <persName>Aliotti</persName> et
                            <persName>Rughittia</persName> mater eorum, relicta quondam suprascripti
                        Aliotti et quondam filia <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/3243">Herici
                                <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs></persName>, (…) investierunt
                                <persName><name ref="Rogerius">Roggierum</name></persName>
                        hospitalarium <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">ospitalis</rs> Sancti Gilii de loco <placeName
                                ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals">Altepascio</placeName></orgName>
                        (…) de tota terra eorum illa que vocatur <placeName ref="#places/3202">Collo
                            della Marca</placeName>, que est prope <placeName ref="#places/3202"
                            >Montem Falconis</placeName>. Que tenet unum caput in via publica, aliut
                        caput tenet in palude, latus unum in rivo qui vocatur Rimoni, aliut in rivo
                        que et iusta terram de <placeName ref="#places/2482">Staffoli</placeName>.
                        (…) Custodes et rectores <foreign>si impegnano a</foreign> reddendi (…) per
                        se vel per suum missum eisdem germanis et matri eorum vel eorum heredes vel
                        eorum misso in qualicumque loco in anno in mense mai soldi tres bon. luc.
                        (…) Prefati germani pro se et pro aliis germanis suis et suprascripta eorum
                        matre obligaverunt se suosque heredes ac proheredes sub pena librarum decem
                        argenti ottimi et consulum et treguanorum luc. (…) Anno dominice
                        incarnationis millesimo centesimo septuagesimo secundo, sexto idus aprelis,
                        indictione quinta. <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Dulcis"
                                >Dulcis</name>
                            <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs></persName> domni imperatoris ibi
                        interfui et memorie causa hec pub. lict. denotavi.</ab>
                </div>
